content: Construction costs for assembly next year, hang with me a second, I'm trying to -- we said we will say in the Q when we file it a little later today, approximately $73 million for full year '23, which is -- which anticipates about $5 million of either $59 million of land sale and/or certain incentive payments on public infrastructure that we would receive in '23 and then an additional $20 million of additional incentive payments probably late '23 or early -- I'd say late '23 right now based on the construction schedule.
